CURRENT PRODUCTION CAPABILITIES

Atlas can currently:

✓ Create and manage inventions

✓ Maintain persistent invention memory

✓ Coordinate executive departments

✓ Delegate work automatically

✓ Generate structured business deliverables

✓ Generate engineering documentation

✓ Maintain Engineering Intelligence

✓ Maintain Native CAD foundations

✓ Maintain Manufacturing Intelligence

✓ Maintain Patent Intelligence foundations

✓ Process uploaded evidence

✓ Build executive briefings

✓ Generate validation materials

✓ Generate investor packages

✓ Generate licensing materials

✓ Generate manufacturing documentation

✓ Coordinate work through conversation

✓ Monitor autonomous execution

✓ Resume work automatically when dependencies clear

--------------------------------------------------------------------

CURRENT LIMITATIONS

Atlas does not yet:

• Publish external content automatically

• Send email campaigns

• Purchase advertising

• File patents

• Spend money

• Generate production STEP files

• Perform native CAD modeling

• Complete live market validation

• Execute financial transactions

These limitations are caused by missing integrations or intentional
authority boundaries—not architectural limitations.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

CURRENT HIGHEST PRIORITY

Simplify the founder experience.

Reduce cognitive load.

Hide implementation details.

Surface outcomes instead of architecture.

Increase autonomous execution.

Only interrupt the founder when human judgment, money, legal authority,
or unavailable external systems require it.

