DOCUMENT MAINTENANCE

This document shall be updated only when one or more of the following
occur:

• A release milestone is completed.

• A major architectural decision is approved.

• Founder validation changes product direction.

• A constitutional principle is amended.

• A new long-term platform capability is adopted.

Minor implementation details should be documented elsewhere and should
not require revision of this Release Master Plan.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

FINAL PRINCIPLE

Atlas exists to help inventors succeed.

Every architectural decision, engineering effort, user experience
improvement, and autonomous capability should move Atlas closer to
becoming a trusted executive partner that founders rely upon throughout
the entire invention journey.

